[center][b]21. كۈلۈپ سۆزلە، قەلبكە يول تاپ[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] Speak with a smile, find the way to hearts.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] Kindness in speech opens doors that logic cannot.

[center][b]22. بىلىم بەرگەن قەدەر ئۆزۈڭمۇ ئۈگىن[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] While teaching, you learn too.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] Teaching reinforces knowledge and deepens understanding.

[center][b]23. تىلسىمات بىلىم ئىچىدە[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] Magic lies within knowledge.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] Real power comes from understanding the world.

[center][b]24. ھاياتتا ئۆگىنىش توختىمايدۇ[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] In life, learning never stops.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] Every stage brings new lessons, and wisdom is endless.

[center][b]25. بىلىمسىز ئەركىنلىك، باشقۇرغىلى بولمايدۇ[/b][/center]  
[b]English:[/b] Freedom without knowledge cannot be governed.  
[b]Explanation:[/b] A free mind needs guidance; ignorance leads to chaos.
